<p>
<note n="0436002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0436002">三＝四【甲】</note>
<note n="0436003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0436003">人＋（也）【甲】</note>
<note n="0436004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0436004">暖＝煖【甲】</note>
